Rendering
---------

- Resource dictionaries
- Transparency
   + Opacity
   + Opacity Masks
- Visual Brush
- Quadratic Bézier curve
- Smooth Cubic Bézier curve
- Elliptical Arc
- Radial gradients when center != origin
- Tile modes (FlipX, FlipY, FlipXY)
- Triangle line cap
- Font props (weight, slant)
